// ==UserScript==
// @name         Alert Messages
// @namespace    http://tampermonkey.net/
// @homepage     https://greasyfork.org/en/users/946530-purefishmonke
// @version      2.3
// @description  sends an alert when you press a certain button on your keyboard
// @downloadURL  https://greasyfork.org/en/scripts/449676-tab-spammer
// @updateURL    https://greasyfork.org/en/scripts/449676-tab-spammer
// @supportURL   https://discord.io/BIGfisHInc
// @author       purefishmonke
